OSPF configuration in layer 3 switch 
ip routing 
router ospd 10
network 10.10.10.0 0.0.0.255 area 0
Add inter-vlan routing in layer 3 switch plus ip dhcp helper address
Vlan 10
Valn 20
Vlan 30                                                   #first write how many vlan in layer 3 switch
Valn 40
Vlan 50                                                    #enter

Int vlan  10                                        #go the  vlan 10
No shutdown
Ip address 192.168.2.1    255.255.255.0           #add gateway of the vlan 10
Ip helper-address    168.129.11.3                       #this is the srever ip 
Exit
Do wr                                                                       #in last after all configure save 
#now same step for each vlan 20,30 and etc
